title: Independent Candidate Hameed-ur-Rehman wins PK-19 election
content:
ISLAMABAD, Feb 9 (APP): An Independent Candidate Hameed-ur-Rehman has won the Khyber Pakhtunkhwa Assembly election from PK-19, Bajour-I by securing 23,044 votes.
According to the unofficial result issued by the Returning Officer/ECP, his runner-up was an Independent Candidate Khalid Khan who bagged 13,571 votes.
Overall votersâ€™ turn-out remained 29.48 per cent.
